NDLEA commissions call centre as FG, EU, UNODC commend Agency for initiative CHAIRMAN/CHIEF EXECUTIVE of the National Drug Law Enforcement Agency (NDLEA), Brig. Gen. Mohammed Buba Marwa (Retd), has said drug users and addicts no longer have excuse not to seek treatment with the commissioning of a modern 24/7 call centre set up to attend to Nigerians from all parts of the country. 